extendedInfo.description: FSB Mobile Banking by Farmers State Bank allows you to bank on the go. It's free to download and offers quick access for managing your bank accounts. Check your balances, pay bills, transfer money, and locate ATMs and banking centers with just a touch. Our native app is fast, secure and free. Use your current login information to start banking today.Features:â¢Check Account Balancesâ¢Transfer funds between accountsâ¢Pay Bills**â¢Find our ATMs and Banking Centers using the GPS system provided by your Android.****Must be an Online Banking Customer**Online customers must first setup transfer and bill pay accounts prior to using these features.***This is limited to locating our banking centers and ATMs. Please refer to your carrier for any fees that may apply.

reviews.title: Quit after update
reviews.comment: It worked fabulous before a recent update now I can\'t even log in! Force closed every time. :(  lg zip
reviews.author: Adele Renner

reviews.title: Out of date
reviews.comment: For a bank that advertises it strives to keep up with technology it really has no way of showing that. This app needs mobile deposit. And my biggest beef is that we need a notification in the app of when our password is going to expire. It shows on the desktop page, but I rarely use it. I use the mobile app for 99% of my banking and frankly I\'m not happy with it. A way to update the password would be nice too.
reviews.author: Darren Engleking
